high_descs: Move forward towards the sofa.
Take one tomato from the sofa.
Turn left, walk towards the microwave in the corner of the room.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside, close it.
Turn around, walk towards the sofa.
Take another tomato from the sofa.
Turn left, walk towards the microwave in the corner of the room.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside, close it.
anns.task_desc: To heat the two tomato's found on the sofa.

high_descs: Head to the sofa on the right.
Pick up the tomato on the right.
Head to the microwave on the left.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
Turn right to reach the sofa.
Pick up the tomato from the sofa.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put two tomatoes in the microwave.

high_descs: Little bit move towards the right side of the couch
Take a middle tomato from the couch
Turn right and walk towards the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the tomato inside it and close the oven
Turn back and walk towards the couch again and stand in front of the couch
Take a first tomato from the couch
Turn right and walk towards the microwave oven again
Open the oven and put the tomato inside it and close the oven
anns.task_desc: Put the tomato in the oven
